---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Capabilities | Foremost Machine, Inc.">
  <section class="section-shell">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Capabilities</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-slate-300">Our team supports commercial buyers that need repeatable quality, responsive communication, and scalable part production.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Precision CNC Milling & Turning</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Complex geometry, production consistency, and tolerance-critical components.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Materials</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Aluminum, steels, stainless, brass, engineering plastics, and customer-specified stock.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Secondary Services</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Deburr, finishing coordination, and inspection documentation ready for your QA workflow.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Production Support</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Forecast collaboration, blanket orders, and practical lead-time planning.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
